[
    {
        "text": "Dyslexia: so what is it all about?",
        "startTime": 31,
        "endTime": 3089,
        "slowStartTime": 197,
        "slowEndTime": 4859
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, dyslexia is a word that is used to describe a difficulty with written language,...",
        "startTime": 3762,
        "endTime": 9033,
        "slowStartTime": 5793,
        "slowEndTime": 13774
    },
    {
        "text": "...organization, and short-term memory.",
        "startTime": 9571,
        "endTime": 12284,
        "slowStartTime": 14507,
        "slowEndTime": 18651
    },
    {
        "text": "However, no one's dyslexia is the same.",
        "startTime": 12943,
        "endTime": 15887,
        "slowStartTime": 19565,
        "slowEndTime": 24056
    },
    {
        "text": "Dyslexia is like a thumbprint,...",
        "startTime": 16295,
        "endTime": 18175,
        "slowStartTime": 24592,
        "slowEndTime": 27488
    },
    {
        "text": "...every print being different.",
        "startTime": 18679,
        "endTime": 20546,
        "slowStartTime": 28168,
        "slowEndTime": 31044
    },
    {
        "text": "Dyslexia is a difference in how the brain works.",
        "startTime": 21640,
        "endTime": 24622,
        "slowStartTime": 32610,
        "slowEndTime": 37158
    },
    {
        "text": "This can have positive effects also.",
        "startTime": 25367,
        "endTime": 27514,
        "slowStartTime": 38200,
        "slowEndTime": 41496
    },
    {
        "text": "Often, dyslexics are good at practical tasks,...",
        "startTime": 28650,
        "endTime": 31541,
        "slowStartTime": 43125,
        "slowEndTime": 47536
    },
    {
        "text": "...whilst many are good communicators or problem solvers.",
        "startTime": 32113,
        "endTime": 35539,
        "slowStartTime": 48320,
        "slowEndTime": 53533
    },
    {
        "text": "It is estimated that about ten percent of the population are dyslexic.",
        "startTime": 36581,
        "endTime": 41117,
        "slowStartTime": 55022,
        "slowEndTime": 61901
    },
    {
        "text": "But being dyslexic does not affect intelligence.",
        "startTime": 41631,
        "endTime": 44557,
        "slowStartTime": 62597,
        "slowEndTime": 67061
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, there are many successful dyslexics in all walks of life.",
        "startTime": 44966,
        "endTime": 49113,
        "slowStartTime": 67599,
        "slowEndTime": 73895
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody finds certain things easier than others.",
        "startTime": 49498,
        "endTime": 52230,
        "slowStartTime": 74397,
        "slowEndTime": 78570
    },
    {
        "text": "And we all have a talent.",
        "startTime": 52671,
        "endTime": 54116,
        "slowStartTime": 79156,
        "slowEndTime": 81399
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just a case of finding what your particular talent is.",
        "startTime": 54774,
        "endTime": 58313,
        "slowStartTime": 82311,
        "slowEndTime": 87695
    },
    {
        "text": "Most dyslexics find a word-based society extremely challenging.",
        "startTime": 59089,
        "endTime": 63352,
        "slowStartTime": 88784,
        "slowEndTime": 95253
    },
    {
        "text": "Self-confidence can be dented if they constantly fail at school.",
        "startTime": 64032,
        "endTime": 67743,
        "slowStartTime": 96198,
        "slowEndTime": 101839
    },
    {
        "text": "Dyslexics need to be taught in a way that matches the way they learn.",
        "startTime": 68975,
        "endTime": 72847,
        "slowStartTime": 103613,
        "slowEndTime": 109496
    },
    {
        "text": "Low self-esteem often holds dyslexics back in life.",
        "startTime": 73639,
        "endTime": 76969,
        "slowStartTime": 110609,
        "slowEndTime": 115678
    },
    {
        "text": "Difficulties with literacy or organizing yourself can cause problems at work, school or college.",
        "startTime": 77648,
        "endTime": 84501,
        "slowStartTime": 116622,
        "slowEndTime": 126976
    },
    {
        "text": "It is important that a dyslexic gets the right support when it's needed...",
        "startTime": 85311,
        "endTime": 89301,
        "slowStartTime": 128116,
        "slowEndTime": 134177
    },
    {
        "text": "...and plays to their strengths whenever possible.",
        "startTime": 89820,
        "endTime": 92100,
        "slowStartTime": 134880,
        "slowEndTime": 138375
    },
    {
        "text": "Relationships with friends and family can be stressful if other people don't understand.",
        "startTime": 92879,
        "endTime": 98429,
        "slowStartTime": 139469,
        "slowEndTime": 147868
    },
    {
        "text": "It really does help to talk so you can all understand how everybody is feeling.",
        "startTime": 99217,
        "endTime": 104447,
        "slowStartTime": 148975,
        "slowEndTime": 156895
    },
    {
        "text": "Being dyslexic is for life.",
        "startTime": 106064,
        "endTime": 107831,
        "slowStartTime": 159246,
        "slowEndTime": 161971
    },
    {
        "text": "There is no quick fix.",
        "startTime": 108209,
        "endTime": 109580,
        "slowStartTime": 162464,
        "slowEndTime": 164595
    },
    {
        "text": "But with determination and support, happiness and success will come.",
        "startTime": 110215,
        "endTime": 115589,
        "slowStartTime": 165473,
        "slowEndTime": 173608
    }
]